OL,3,CTipper truck driver found guilty after
OL,4,Ccrashing into M5 gantry
OL,6,FA tipper truck driver has been
OL,7,Fconvicted of dangerous driving after
OL,8,Fhe crashed into a motorway gantry.
OL,10,FBristol Crown Court heard Anthony
OL,11,FBaker, aged 48 and from Downend,
OL,12,Ffailed to lower the tipper truck
OL,13,Fbefore he drove his 32-tonne vehicle
OL,14,Fonto the M5 on 2 March last year.
OL,16,FThe jury heard how the tipper was
OL,17,Ffully raised when it hit the overhead
OL,18,Fsigns.
