OL,3,CTipper truck driver found guilty after
OL,4,Ccrashing into M5 gantry
OL,6,FBaker had delivered a load of stone to
OL,7,Fa site in Cribbs Causeway. Afterwards,
OL,8,Fthe court heard, he had failed to
OL,9,Fswitch the Power Take Off (PTO) lever,
OL,10,Fwhich would have lowered the tipper.
OL,12,FCCTV showed the truck driving from the
OL,13,Fsite to the M5. A dashboard camera,
OL,14,Ffilmed by another motorist, showed the
OL,15,Fmoment before the crash.
OL,17,FBaker told the court that after making
OL,18,Fhis delivery, he had engaged the lever
OL,19,Fand felt the tipper start to lower,
OL,20,Fand started to drive off.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/5
