OL,3,CTipper truck driver found guilty after
OL,4,Ccrashing into M5 gantry
OL,6,FHe said he thought it would have been
OL,7,Fin the correct position before he
OL,8,Freached the public highway. But he was
OL,9,Fmistaken - he said he had not looked
OL,10,Fin his rear mirror.
OL,12,FPC Ian Hudson, of Avon and Somerset's
OL,13,Froads policing unit, said: "The
OL,14,Fconsequences of this collision could
OL,15,Fhave been catastrophic had the matrix
OL,16,Fsign hit a vehicle travelling at 70mph
OL,17,For the gantry collapsed onto a live
OL,18,Fmotorway.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/5
