OL,3,CTipper truck driver found guilty after
OL,4,Ccrashing into M5 gantry
OL,6,F"Anthony Baker's failure to perform
OL,7,Feven a basic check that the lorry bed
OL,8,Fhad been lowered is inexplicable and
OL,9,Fput other road users in danger.
OL,11,F"Road safety is something everyone
OL,12,Fneeds to have at the forefront of
OL,13,Ftheir minds when they get behind the
OL,14,Fwheel of any vehicle."
OL,16,FThe motorway was closed for 14 hours
OL,17,Fto ensure the gantry was safe. The
OL,18,Fmotorway was then closed the following
OL,19,Fweekend to allow the gantry to be
OL,20,Fremoved.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/5
