OL,3,CTipper truck driver found guilty after
OL,4,Ccrashing into M5 gantry
OL,6,FThe court heard Baker had an
OL,7,Funblemished driving record and tested
OL,8,Fnegative for drugs and alcohol in his
OL,9,Fbloodstream.
OL,11,FBaker had told the jury he admitted
OL,12,Fthe lesser charge of careless driving,
OL,13,Fbut the jury convicted him of
OL,14,Fdangerous driving. He will be
OL,15,Fsentenced in August.
